                            <comment id="13659347" author="slebresne" created="Thu, 16 May 2013 08:08:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;lgtm, +1.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Makes me think it might simplify things a bit to use range tombstones in dropFromSchema. And maybe we could start using CQL3 queries (with processInternal) to avoid having to deal with row markers manually? But anyway, we can definitively do that later. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13659523" author="iamaleksey" created="Thu, 16 May 2013 13:39:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yeah, thought about range tombstones here as well yesterday. But, later.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
